org.apache.hadoop.registry.server.services

Interface MicroZookeeperServiceKeys

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MicroZookeeperService

    public interface MicroZookeeperServiceKeys
    Service keys for configuring the MicroZookeeperService. These are not used in registry clients or the RM-side service, so are kept separate.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String DEFAULT_ZKSERVICE_HOST
      Default host to serve on -this is localhost as it is the only one guaranteed to be available: "localhost".

      Key to define the JAAS context for the ZK service: "hadoop.registry.zk.service.service.jaas.context".

      Should failed SASL clients be allowed: "hadoop.registry.zk.service.allow.failed.sasl.clients"? Default is the ZK default: true
